   Information for Local Governments

   The Office of Financial Management serves local governments in a
   variety of ways. OFM provides population estimates and forecasts and
   also publishes information on county finances. Available online are the
   OFM Population Trends and Forecasts and the Washington State Data Book.

   Other useful publications are also accessible online. Accessing OFM's
   information is simply a click away.
